    <bioghist id="aspace_ff7931d9de37dd8c5239148802053c67">
      <head>Biographical Note</head>
      <p>The Rev. William Graham was a Presbyterian minister and one of the founders of Liberty Hall
        Academy (later Washington and Lee University); He performed many scientific experiments, one
        of which led him to the patent on the modern fire extinguisher.</p>
    </bioghist>
